data.description:
Welcome To 149 Patchen Ave
All showings and open houses are by appointment. Call to schedule your showing.
149 Patchen Ave is a 2 Family Townhouse located in Bedford-Stuyvesant.
The home in total has 15 rooms, 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, 2 kitchens, 3 fireplaces, unfinished basement and a backyard. The first floor is a 1 bedroom apartment with direct access to the backyard. The second floor is a 1 bedroom apartment with a half bedroom that can be a home office or a closet. The third floor has 2 bedrooms also with a half bedroom that can be a home office or a closet.
